et-container\">\n\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Privacy Policy<\/h2>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-a1b2346 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"a1b2346\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;content_width&quot;:&quot;boxed&quot;}\" data-core-v316-plus=\"true\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-643e397 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"643e397\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Tenderhearts Healthcare (&#8220;we,&#8221; &#8220;us,&#8221; or &#8220;our&#8221;) is committed to protecting the privacy of our website visitors (&#8220;you&#8221;). This Privacy Policy explains what information we collect about you, how we use it, and your choices regarding your information.<\/p><p><strong>Information We Collect:<\/strong><\/p><ul><li><strong>Appointment Information:<\/strong> When you schedule an appointment, we collect your name, contact information (email address and phone number), and reason for visit.<br \/><strong>Referral Information:<\/strong> If you submit a referral, we collect the names and contact information of both the referring party and the person being referred.<\/li><li><strong>Website Usage Information:<\/strong> We may collect information about your visit to our website, such as the pages you visit, the time and date of your visit, and the browser you use. We may use cookies and other tracking technologies to collect this information.<\/li><\/ul><p>\u00a0<\/p><p><strong>How We Use Your Information:<\/strong><\/p><ul><li><strong>Appointment Scheduling:<\/strong> We use your appointment information to schedule and confirm your appointments and communicate with you about them.<\/li><li><strong>Referral Processing:<\/strong> We use your referral information to process referrals and track their progress.<\/li><li><strong>Website Improvement:<\/strong> We use website usage information to improve our website and make it more user-friendly.<\/li><\/ul><p>\u00a0<\/p><p><strong>Information Sharing and Disclosure:<\/strong><\/p><ul><li><strong>Legal Requirements:<\/strong> We may disclose your information if required by law, such as in response to a court order or subpoena.<\/li><li><strong>Emergency Situations:<\/strong> We may disclose your information in emergencies to protect the safety of you or others.<\/li><\/ul><p>\u00a0<\/p><p><strong>Your Choices:<\/strong><\/p><ul><li><strong>Cookies:<\/strong> You can choose to disable cookies in your browser settings. However, some features of our website may not work properly if you disable cookies.<br \/>Marketing Communications: You can opt out of receiving marketing communications from us by clicking the &#8220;unsubscribe&#8221; link in any marketing email you receive from us.<\/li><li><strong>Access and Correction:<\/strong> You can request access to and correction of your information by contacting us at [<a href=\"mailto:info@thhcs.com\">info@thhcs.com<\/a>].<br \/>Data Security:<\/li><li>We take reasonable measures to protect your information from unauthorized access, disclosure, or alteration. However, no website is completely secure, and we cannot guarantee the security of your information.<\/li><\/ul><p>\u00a0<\/p><p><strong>Changes to this Privacy Policy:<\/strong><\/p><p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will post any changes on our website.<\/p><p>\u00a0<\/p><p><strong>Contact Us:<\/strong><\/p><p>If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at [<a href=\"mailto:info@thhcs.com\">info@thhcs.com<\/a>].<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Privacy Policy You Data, Our S